title: Pumpkin Walnut and Raisin Cookies
ingredients: ['110g margarine', '275g dark brown soft sugar', '2 eggs', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '375g pumpkin puree', '310g plain flour', '4 teaspoons baking powder', '1/2 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1/2 teaspoon ground nutmeg', '145g raisins', '115g chopped walnuts']
